//TITLE:	Tech Day 4 at Southampton
//DESCRIPTION:	A Southampton tech day for Student Robotics on the 19th March 2016.
//KEYWORDS:	Tech Day

Tech Day 4 at Southampton
=========================

Join us in Southampton for the fourth Student Robotics
[tech day](/events/tech_days) of the year, where you can work on your robots
with the help of volunteers and other teams.

What: A [tech day](/events/tech_days).

When: 9am to 5pm, 19<sup>th</sup> March 2016

Where: The Design Studio in
[Building 177](http://data.southampton.ac.uk/building/177.html) on the
University of Southampton's Boldrewood Campus.
(Also see [the campus website](http://www.southampton.ac.uk/about/visit/getting-to-our-campuses.page#boldrewood).)

Who: All Student Robotics teams are welcome to attend. Please inform us if your
team is coming by emailing <southampton@studentrobotics.org>.

Food: There is a nearby garage, a small Co-op along Burgess Road and a Costa
approximately 15 minutes walk away.

