Parking
-------

Car parking is available on Boldrewood campus for free as we have visitor permits available. There will be volunteers available to direct you on the site.

Computing requirements
----------------------

The event is taking place in an engineering design studio so access to desktop
computers is unavailable. We will be providing laptops to teams which need them,
but we highly recommend that at least one member of your team brings their own.
